sources.title: It Happened Out West (1937) WESTERN
sources.description:
Stars: Paul Kelly, Judith Allen, Johnny Arthur 
Director: Howard Bretherton

A bank employee, tasked with telling an Arizona rancher her property is worthless, gets suspicious when her foreman agrees -- turns out his banker boss and the foreman know there's silver on her land!

metadata.Plot: Bank employee assigned to tell Arizona rancher her property is no good gets suspicious when her foreman agrees. Turns out his banker boss and the foreman know there's silver on that property.
metadata.Actors: Paul Kelly, Judith Allen, Johnny Arthur
